        "product_description": {
            "value": "Bring the magic of Disney Junior to hairstyling with the Minnie Mouse Bowtique Hair Accessory Gift Set. This adorable 11-piece collection is perfect for little ones who love Minnie Mouse and enjoy dressing up their hair. The set includes a comb, brush, barrettes, clips, and hair ties, all neatly stored in a fun, reusable Minnie-themed backpack that's easy to carry and store. Decorated in cheerful pink with signature Minnie Mouse styling, this gift set encourages pretend play and helps toddlers and young girls develop their sense of style. Designed for kids ages 3 and up, it makes a wonderful birthday present, holiday gift, or party favor for any Minnie Mouse fan. The lightweight, kid-friendly accessories are sized just right for small hands, making everyday hairstyling a delightful and imaginative experience. Whether getting ready for school, playtime, or a special occasion, this Disney Junior Minnie Mouse Bowtique set adds a touch of enchantment to any little girl's routine.",
